BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 237.15 Td (The international community has not been silent on Addressing the Security Implications) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 222.65 Td (of Climate-Induced Displacement and Resource Scarcity. Earlier resolutions, conferences,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 208.15 Td (and frameworks have laid important groundwork, even if implementation has often fallen) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 193.65 Td (short of what was promised. Research which instruments are most relevant to ESC —) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 179.15 Td (including any prior actions taken by this committee or the bodies it answers to — and) Tj ET
